  "description": "<p>The School of\nEconomics at Singapore Management University has openings for tenure-track\nappointment at the rank of Presidential\nAssistant Professor under the Presidential Early\nCareer Professorship (SMU-PEP) Scheme. The school invites applications from outstanding\ncandidates with teaching and research interests in all fields of Economics.</p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u>Application Requirements</u></a></p><p>•                \nCV</p><p>•                \nTeaching Evaluations</p><p>•                \nResearch Papers</p><p>•                \nConsolidated candidate’s statement including an overview of candidate’s\nresearch, teaching and service (up to 6 pages)</p><p>•                \nCover Letter</p>",
